                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6904" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MGEC-0076</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12795 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东方风起：东风新能源汽车全产业链数智化转型与升级</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Wind is Rising from East: Digital-Intelligence Transformation and Upgrading of Dongfeng New Energy Vehicle&#39;s Whole Industry Chain</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘凯，苗雯，孙妍，田媛，王岩岩</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中南财经政法大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东风汽车集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化转型；产业数字化；竞争战略；全产业链；新能源汽车</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital transformation, Industrial digitization, Competitive strategy, Whole industry chain, New energy vehicles</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国汽车工业正经历百年未有之大变局，传统车企如何在技术“卡脖子”与“双碳”目标双重压力下，利用数智化机遇实现全产业链转型升级是企业战略管理相关课程教学中值得解构的问题。本案例以东风集团在“双循环”新发展格局下开拓新能源汽车细分赛道为主线，讲述了企业如何在产业链的上、中、下游及后市场利用技术与模式创新进行“补链”、“强链”、“扩链”与“延链”，通过数字赋能全产业链，实现“弯道超车”的故事。案例主要分为“‘补’齐短板，得芯应手”、“‘强’化优势，数智赋能”、“‘扩’宽市场，内外联动”、“‘延’展无限，价值攀升”四个部分，分别展现了东风集团新能源汽车在研发、制造、营销及后市场四个产业链环节上开展数智化转型的动因、方式以及成效，真实再现了企业数智化转型过程中的战略决策与经营策略。案例通过鲜活的语言、丰富的资料和详实的数据将产业链理论、数字经济、经营层基本竞争战略、营销策略等融入到生动的叙事之中，让学生在解读中国企业故事的过程中学习理解企业战略决策，同时也能厚植企业发展融入国家发展战略的大局观念，培养学生投身社会发展的使命与担当。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">China&#39;s automobile industry is experiencing great changes unprecedented in a century. Under the dual pressure of technology &quot;stuck neck&quot; and &quot;dual carbon&quot; goals, how traditional car companies can take advantage of digital and intelligent opportunities to realize the transformation and upgrading of the entire industry chain is a course teaching related to corporate strategic management questions worth deconstructing. This case takes Dongfeng Group&#39;s development of new energy vehicle subdivision track as the main line under the new development pattern of &quot;double cycle&quot;, and describes the story of how enterprises use technology and mode innovation to &quot;Complement the chain&quot;, &quot;Strengthen the chain&quot;, &quot;Expand the chain&quot; and &quot;Extend the chain&quot; in the upstream, mid-stream, downstream and after-market of the industrial chain, and achieve &quot;Overtaking on the curve&quot; through digital empowerment of the whole industrial chain. The case is mainly divided into &quot;&#39;Fixing&#39; shortcomings, getting cores handy&quot;, &quot;&#39;Strengthening&#39; advantages, empowering digital intelligence&quot;, &quot;&#39;Expanding&#39; market, internal and external linkages&quot;, &quot;&#39;Extending&#39; infinitely, increasing the value&quot; four parts, respectively shows the motivation, method and effect of the digital and intelligent transformation of Dongfeng Group&#39;s new energy vehicles in the four industrial chain links of R&amp;D, manufacturing, marketing and aftermarket, and truly reproduces the strategic decisions and business strategies in the process of digital-intelligence transformation. The case integrates industry chain theory, digital economy, basic management competition strategy, and marketing strategy into vivid narratives through vivid language, rich materials and detailed data, allowing students to learn corporate strategic decisions in the process of interpreting Chinese corporate stories, at the same time also can strengthen the overall concept of integrating enterprise development into national development strategy, and cultivate students&#39; mission and responsibility for social development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业战略管理》、《产业经济学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新能源相关概念及新能源汽车分类；PESTEL模型；VRIO模型；产业数字化转型价值链；产业数字化转型能力评估体系；产业链“微笑曲线”</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
